_sText:
This map was ported around 2005. This port, despite the fact that it is a PORT, is very developed and improved compared to the original. Here, Source entities and some improvements are used, primarily displacements are used, as well as puddles and other effects in some places.
This is one of the best examples of how to port maps! Improving them, because ordinary ports are not always of high quality and do not require much effort.


This is a port with remastered elements.
